{"tid":1142834,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"百威英博證實來港上市 傳籌390億元 或今年最大","createTime":"2019-05-07T10:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T19:01:04.000Z","uid":28765,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"103e46e0d0a17b2cb8145c63fbdb08cb7cf65775","tid":1142834,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T10:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190507/large/1557223940_5050.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190507%2Flarge%2F1557223940_5050.jpg&h=b84847b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n百威英博證實分拆亞太業務來港上市<br />\n<br />\n全球最大啤酒商百威英博證實，正在考慮將其亞太業務的少數股權上市，並將在港交所(388)掛牌上市，以減少債務及在該地區尋求收購機會。前此有傳百威英博目標今夏來港掛牌，集資金額高達50億美元（約390億港元）<br />\n百威英博首季核心盈利(EBITDA)為49.9億美元，增長8.2%，低於市場預期的50.6億美元，但是公司5個季度以來的最快盈利增長。<br />\n百威英博自2016年以超過1000億美元收購SABMiller後，其淨負債比率持續上升。該公司在10月將股息減半，以保留資金來償還債務。標普全球評級在3月表示可能會降低其信用評級；去年年底，穆迪已把其評級下調。<br />\n今年1月已有傳百威英博會分拆上市，並屬意香港為上市首選。百威英博亞洲業務估值高達700億美元（約5,460億港元），市傳公司尋求出售20%股份集資。<br />\n百威英博在亞太區經營的主要品牌，包括百威、Corona、時代、Hoegaarden、樂飛、哈爾濱、雪津啤酒等。旗下啤酒品牌Corona去年全球收入增17.6%，中國為Corona第一出口市場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190507/59574338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F59574338&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=a9b16038\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F59574338&h=8eb5e0f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190507/59574338</a>"},{"pid":"eab7a3594c8da592cd611261cbb9022669848cbe","tid":1142834,"uid":34013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:56:03.000Z","msg":"同股同權上就抽小小玩下"},{"pid":"4976134cf14210c437f5b08a4dc8eb9071109092","tid":1142834,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ggvfofU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FggvfofU.jpg&h=ae6b6f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf626358b6505b375bccedb1ed88abcbd296e479","tid":1142834,"uid":246729,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"等睇數簿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9152175555576665797b7e069d065ef679a91ea3","tid":1142834,"uid":66933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:57:37.000Z","msg":"抽"},{"pid":"5a2b5ac6031e606512e7fd8b5087a92d208d7a56","tid":1142834,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ggvfofU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FggvfofU.jpg&h=ae6b6f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大部分都唔好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f9cf2961e5413d1605e66956153af68a737ada","tid":1142834,"uid":246729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf626358b6505b375bccedb1ed88abcbd296e479","tid":1142834,"uid":246729,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"等睇數簿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T19:01:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1150350/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1150350/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}